Package: LongcellLite
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight BAM-Based Single-Cell Long-Read Quantification
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Wenxu Yuan
Maintainer: Wenxu Yuan <yuanwenxu123@gmail.com>
Description: A lightweight single-cell long-read RNA-seq quantification package
    that starts from mapped BAM files with pre-assigned cell barcodes and UMIs.
    The first version focuses on annotation preparation, BAM read extraction,
    read-level isoform reconstruction, UMI-level isoform quantification, and
    optional transcript-matrix generation while reusing Longcellsrc for core
    low-level computations.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
